creator: Play Vertex
descriptionHtml:
It’s Open Season - join this hunting game today!

Best FPS (first person shooter) game for target rabbit shooting.

Let's go toward the real safari forest for hare hunting animals. Are you crazy about making real Rabbits prey? If Yes, this game is just for you to get target huntsman experience by trapping hares. Most realistic new action & full of thrilling game, Rabbit Hunting Sweet Challenge, Shoting Games FPS for Android Devices. If you want to become a professional bunnies target shooter then game provides a chance for you to hunts & shoot the crazy rabbits. You have played many animals shooting games but this one contains different killing shot features like to killing a bunny you can use given guns. It is all about the precise hunt of running and idle rabbits, aiming too quickly and shoot at the right time. Develop your skills as a bunny shooter by hunts down as possible in a limited time. You must have to set a very high target to kill all hares.

Rabbit Hunting Challenge is the hunter simulator game in the forest for the professional shooter of safari hare fishing game. Hunt the specific number of real rabbits with limited time to complete the waves of the location. Kill to the animal by aiming and keeping good shoot from guns. All bunnies or animals should be hunted by you. Enter the forest with modern FPS Guns like Bow, Crossbow, HMG (heavy machine gun) and Gatling Mini Machine Gun and start your trapping in this wild bunny jungle pursuit. Try to be master of crossbow hare trapping & shoting by becoming an Animal Hunter & by playing hares gunning which is one of the best hunting game.

Bunny snipping in a jungle is the most beautiful, addictive & thrilling action hobby of trapping hare in the jungle. This game will test your skill of gunning & fishing. Download this free game on your android phone and start playing this amazing 3d wild shooting game. It involves many exciting levels that include the increasing difficulty level with each increasing levels.

REAL ANIMALS
Travel on realistic and huntsman locations and hunt to real animals that are in this hunting game. This gunfire games just went global!

SHOOT LIKE A BEST HUNTER
Establish or develop a steady hand, sights up to your line, and use your master skills to take the perfect shot and then kill.

BUILD YOUR ARMORY OR WEAPONS
Collect to your firearms with scopes as you are expert or perfect in your weapons for each hunt and kill.
Features

- Stunning rabbits & chickens (don't hunt chickens) and high-quality 3D graphics.
- Realistic controls for the best target hunting experience.
- Exciting challenging fishing levels
- Best hunter experience by gunning animals in real jungle Environment.
- Immersive gameplay physics.
- Optimal and perfect 3D Forest environment.
- Shoting from a good and comfort point.
- Breathtaking realistic safari jungle environment near hills.

Download on your Android smartphones or tablets and have unlimited fun snipping hares. We greatly recommend you to play rabbit shooting game and rate us 5 star and suggestions to improve the game are most welcome.
